    "body": "stumbled on this was very helpful, just a suggestion, ppl often use dashes in cluster names:\r\n```\r\n[kubernetes]\r\nformat = '[☸](blue) [$context]($style) \\($namespace\\) '\r\ndisabled = false\r\n# Shorten EKS clusters to only the important part of their name\r\n[[kubernetes.contexts]]\r\ncontext_pattern = 'arn.*\\/(?P<cluster>[\\w\\/-]+)'\r\ncontext_alias = \"$cluster\"\r\nstyle = 'green'\r\n\r\n``` ",
